- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper also deals with DoS attacks and their impact on the communication network, which is a security issue. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper deals with communication networks and their impact on control systems, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper deals with data rates and their impact on the stability of control systems, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper does not directly deal with AI, but the use of control systems and networked communication can be relevant to AI applications.
